		<hr size="1">Under 3K is going to limit your choices a bit.</P><P>I don't know what the prices are like on your server, but you might think about:</P><P>Centi Shortsword 12/25 (Primary or secondary)<BR>Centi Longsword 24/27 (Primary, unless you have a faster weapon, then secondary)<BR>Waksashi of the Frozen Skies 6/22 (Primary)<BR>Short Sword of the Ykesha 8/24 (Primary by preference, secondary if you have to)<BR>Smouldering Brand 9/22 (Primary)<BR>Shaded Dagger 11/22 (Primary or Secondary)</P><P>Like Kingsize said, I'd stay away from the Lammy until your high 40s.</P><P>And yeah.. There's nothing wrong with Crafted armor. Don't be intimidated by all these twinks running around in Cobalt. Learn your trade and you'll be at least as good a Warrior as any of them, if not better.</P><P>--<BR>Rafal B'Fereign, Bard of the 30th Song<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=78104" target=_new">Tarsk Longstrider</a>, Champion of the Wolves o' the North<BR>Xev</P><P>"Okay. We got enough youth. How about a fountain of SMART?"</P><P>Message edited by: Rafal (4/23/2002 6:18:50 AM)<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
